Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:46.85,DefaultCN-2202,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:49.76,DefaultCN-2202,,0,0,0,,我们将希望寄托于那艘船上
