Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:21:59.20,DefaultCN-2202,,0,0,0,,立刻给我接海底船坞！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:01.98,DefaultCN-2202,,0,0,0,,大和号……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.71,0:22:15.74,DefaultCN-2202,,0,0,0,,啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:18.15,DefaultCN-2202,,0,0,0,,啊！
